Package: BOLD.NODE
Title: Search and Explore BOLD Dataset Releases Efficiently
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sameer", "Padhye", , "spadhye@uoguelph.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(c("Spencer", "K."), "Monckton", , "smonckto@uoguelph.ca", role = "aut"),
    person("Dirk", "Steinke", , "dsteinke@uoguelph.ca", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides efficient tools for exploring and transforming
    the Barcode of Life Data Systems (BOLD) data packages on local
    machines. It enables fast local querying of the data packages without 
    relying on live API calls. Results can be easily converted into formats
    compatible with widely used R packages and third party tools.
